 shape that’s just right for you. Our back sleepers especially really liked these pillows because they’re a good thickness with comfortable support. One of our back sleepers uses a CPAP machine at night and reported that the Beckham pillow does a good job supporting their neck and upper body and doesn’t interfere with their machine, positions or sleep patterns at all.","Our side sleepers gave mixed reviews – some liked the down-like support, but others felt this pillow didn’t conform well enough to their neck. Our stomach sleepers said the Beckham pillows were too full for them and they felt like they were suffocating because of how much their head fell into the pillow. They prefer the <a href=\"/health/wellness/best-pillows/isotonic-indulgence-review/\">Isotonic Indulgence</a>.","We tested the standard size pillows, but the Beckham Hotel Gel Pillows also come in queen and king sizes. All of them cost under $50 and are best sellers on Amazon. There isn’t a warranty that comes with these pillows, but you do have 30 days to try them out or return them. "]},"id":"18c8bd08-abb7-4168-897d-f93d7b455c3c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"2d4a272a-ad84-4dc1-96d8-6d56b784ec7a","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Beckham Hotel Gel Pillow comes in a two pack for under $50. They’re filled with a down alternative that’s hypoallergenic and gives good, soft and comfortable support. We don’t recommend it for stomach sleepers, and some side sleepers felt their pillows didn’t conform well enough to the shape of their necks. Also, you don’t get a warranty with the Beckham pillow, though you do have 30 days to return it. "]},"id":"e2584f22-ee7c-4bfa-84d4-ac0defceec35","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_70334","url":"/beckham-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-contributor","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-contributor","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Contributor","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16